    slug: "what-early-recovery-looks-like-for-families",
    title: "What Early Recovery Really Looks Like: A Family Guide to the First 90 Days",
    excerpt: "Wondering what happens after your loved one enters treatment? Learn what early recovery really looks like—and how families can help without enabling—from interventionist Katie Barr.",
    date: "2026-04-26",
    author: "Katie Barr, CIP, LCDCi",
